    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its original factory luster without a single scratch or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is pristine, with leather upholstery that looks and feels brand new and all electronic features functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is impeccable, having been meticulously serviced and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from one on a new car lot.",
