    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable project car or a basic set of wheels to get you started? This vehicle is priced to sell and perfect for someone who isn't afraid to put in a little elbow grease! While it definitely shows its age and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great opportunity for a budget-conscious buyer with some handy skills to bring it back to life.",
